item.content:
&lt;p&gt;A slow growing Large solid cystic mass of size 25×15 cms weighing 8 kgs removed from the abdomen of a 74 yrs old female patient. The tumour arises from body of stomach and called as GIST. The patient presented with Abdominal dissension and significant weight loss.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
